  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And afterward Hezron went in to the daughter of Machir the father of Gilead,.... Which Machir was the son of Manasseh, and Gilead was his grandson, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Numbers 26:29",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the Targum is,\"but he enticed a virgin, the daughter of Machir;''which suggests, that he committed fornication with her, though he afterwards married her; her name is not mentioned; to me it seems to be Abiah, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 2:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and whom the Targum there calls the daughter of Machir: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "whom he married when he was sixty years old; the Targum is sixty six; this seems to be his last wife: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and she bare him Segub; the same name with the youngest son of Hiel, who rebuilt Jericho, 1 Kings 16:34. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and she bare him Segub; the same name with the youngest son of Hiel, who rebuilt Jericho, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "1 Kings 16:34",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
